{"tid":2446062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全港萬幾個醫生　藍絲醫生聯署　人數暴跌　僅餘約100人","createTime":"2021-03-14T06:58:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T03:53:44.000Z","uid":261647,"like":79,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"ebe27683b15153aff1f13e1e965987d1a8fb4aca","tid":2446062,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T06:58:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nostakemedicalstudent/posts/268138014869390\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnostakemedicalstudent%2Fposts%2F268138014869390&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfIWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=3eeb0ea9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/nostakemedicalstudent/posts/268138014869390</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aUDt8dX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaUDt8dX.jpg&h=d13f090c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：No Stake 醫學生<br />\n<br />\n【 藍絲醫生聯署：人數暴跌，暨南大學作救兵 】<br />\n<br />\n一如既往，呢個支持人大送香港「上路」嘅聯署，係唔會有任何正式Soft-copy放上網，大家Google係唔會搵到嘅。<br />\n<br />\n但我作為愛國陣營一份子，深受感動，覺得有必要同廣大藍營朋友一齊分享呢份喜悅，親自人手逐個名打返出黎。記得大家揀醫生睇嘅時候支持以下藍絲同路人。全聯署圖見Comment。<br />\n<br />\n仲有，雖然字體已經放到好大，但都填唔滿呢頁全頁廣告，於是聰明嘅佢地，仲諗到可以加埋「暨南大學同學會」、「中山醫科大學校友會」、「政府軍部醫院華員職工會」入去填位，認真犀利。<br />\n<br />\n題外話：2019年嘅撐警聯署有500位醫生，曾經有網民整合左佢地嘅執業、診所資訊等，等大家揀醫生睇嘅時候可作參考，支持佢地。但部份連去嗰個Excel檔Link已經疑似比人Report到用唔到啦（Comment仲有朋友有條用到嘅Link）。點解咁驚？<br />\n<br />\n又，唔知點解今次聯署少咁多人？好失望，點解大家愛國嘅熱誠咁唔堅定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/posts/4029457200427316\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup%2Fposts%2F4029457200427316&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfIWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=76e6cf5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/posts/4029457200427316</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：前線科技人員<br />\n<br />\n全港萬幾個醫生，得百幾個愛國，唔怪之要引入非本地醫生（早幾年仲叫海外醫生，分別係咩，自己諗）"},{"pid":"024c95b12a1efe0a4329fc9709459ae9fdb2444f","tid":2446062,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T07:39:01.000Z","msg":"名單呢?"},{"pid":"51d754c12e9c5c5a92f2318780dc4043b66ca715","tid":2446062,"uid":3776,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T07:42:29.000Z","msg":"其餘400個去左邊"},{"pid":"13de08d9de849dd5c2c9822d54980ce7c94bb836","tid":2446062,"uid":25916,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T07:44:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad2bce848b22a3acf90b2caf0df62f9c1d3e43a","tid":2446062,"uid":6799,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"13de08d9de849dd5c2c9822d54980ce7c94bb836","tid":2446062,"uid":25916,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T07:44:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T07:46:12.000Z","msg":"有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72705df0b052a7686306d723ebfa0bddb2c6fd19","tid":2446062,"uid":29726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T07:48:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c2585ed75341584167a712637b61cbe6fd9a78","tid":2446062,"uid":63253,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"51d754c12e9c5c5a92f2318780dc4043b66ca715","tid":2446062,"uid":3776,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T07:42:29.000Z","msg":"其餘400個去左邊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T07:48:43.000Z","msg":"去左排隊打復必泰"},{"pid":"c1ea39d60edc9121b7178e2a7da0ee23fdc3ef40","tid":2446062,"uid":79563,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"d4c2585ed75341584167a712637b61cbe6fd9a78","tid":2446062,"uid":63253,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"51d754c12e9c5c5a92f2318780dc4043b66ca715","tid":2446062,"uid":3776,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T07:42:29.000Z","msg